---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy — Wychwood Partners" description="Privacy policy.">
  <main class="shell py-14">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
    <h1>Privacy</h1>
    <div class="mt-6 space-y-6 text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))]">
      <p>
        Wychwood Partners respects your privacy. This website collects minimal personal information
        necessary to respond to inquiries and schedule conversations.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[rgb(var(--text))]">Information we may collect</h2>
      <p>
        If you contact us or schedule a call we may receive information such as your name, email address,
        company information, and any details you choose to include in messages or scheduling notes.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[rgb(var(--text))]">Scheduling services</h2>
      <p>
        When you book a call through our scheduling link, your information is processed through
        Google Appointment Scheduling. Your information is handled according to Google’s privacy
        policies and terms of service.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[rgb(var(--text))]">How information is used</h2>
      <p>
        Information submitted through this website is used solely to respond to inquiries,
        schedule conversations, and determine whether working together may be appropriate.
        Wychwood Partners does not sell or share personal information for marketing purposes.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[rgb(var(--text))]">Website hosting</h2>
      <p>
        This website is hosted by Vercel. Server logs may automatically collect basic technical
        information such as IP address, browser type, and access times for operational and
        security purposes.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[rgb(var(--text))]">Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this privacy policy you can contact Wychwood Partners through
        the contact information provided on this website.
      </p>
    </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
